Privacy Policy for QR ScanNGen

Effective Date: 16 Aug, 2024

QR ScanNGen is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines the types of information we collect, how we use and protect it, and your rights regarding your data.

1. Information We Collect:
- Usage Data: We collect data related to your usage of the app, including the types of QR codes generated or scanned.
- Device Information: We collect no information about your device.
- Storage Access: The app requests permission to access your deviceâ€™s storage to save or load QR codes.

2. How We Use Your Information:
- App Functionality: To generate and scan QR codes, store history, and provide other app features

3. Data Sharing and Disclosure:
- Third-Party Services: We do not share your personal information with third parties.

4. Data Security:
We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your information. However, no method of transmission or storage is completely secure.

5. Your Rights:
- Access and Control: You can access, update, or delete your data from the app, just by uninstalling the app as all the data that app have is only on your device.

6. Changes to this Privacy Policy:
We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. We will notify you of any changes by updating the effective date.

7. Contact Us:
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at team.cuboidinc@gmail.com

By using QR ScanNGen, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.
